{"word":"H5161 - נֶחֱלָמִי - Nechĕlâmîy - nekh-el-aw-mee' - Nehelamite","slug":"H5161","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">נֶחֱלָמִי</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>Nechĕlâmîy"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>nekh-el-aw-mee'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Nehelamite"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05E0;&#x05D7;&#x05DC;&#x05DE;&#x05D9; - neche&#x0306;la&#x0302;m&#x0131;&#x0302;y</b> - <i>nekh-el-aw-mee'</i><p/>Apparently a patronymic from an unused name (apparently passive participle of <a href=\"#/H2492\">H2492</a>); <i>dreamed</i>; a <i>Nechelamite</i>, or descendant of Nechlam: - Nehelamite."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H5158\">H5158</a>, <a href=\"#/H5160\">H5160</a>"}]}